Open Access Publishing in Africa: Advancing Research Outputs to Global Visibility
Ezema, Ifeanyi J ; Onyancha, Omwoyo Bosire . African Journal of Library, Archives & Information Science ; Ibadan  Vol. 27, Iss. 2,  (Oct 2017): 97-115.
Publisher logo. Links to publisher website, opened in a new window.
